Just ideas for things to do for everyone stuck at home during December:
• Bake some Christmassy food
• Walks/ Drives to see local Christmas lights
• Get involved donating/ with charities
• Making a Christmas Eve box for a loved one
• Host a zoom call Christmas party/ quiz
• Movie nights
• Games nights
• Christmas wreath making competition
• Hot chocolate & marshmallow night around a bonfire
• Winter photo shoots
• Countryside walks
• Make essential gift bag for the homeless
• Festive karaoke night
• Make a playlist of your favourite festive songs
• Do a Christmas scavenger hunt/ who stole Christmas?
